																			<span class="SG_txtb">标签：</span>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%D0%C7%D7%F9%A1%A2%C3%FC%C0%ED%A1%A2&by=tag" target="_blank">星座、命理、</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%BD%A1%BF%B5&by=tag" target="_blank">健康</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%B7%E7%CB%AE&by=tag" target="_blank">风水</a></h3>
																																<h3><a href="http://search.sina.com.cn/?c=blog&q=%CE%C4%BB%AF&by=tag" target="_blank">文化</a></h3>
																												</td>
									<td class="blog_class">
																			<span class="SG_txtb">分类：</span>
										<a target="_blank" href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/articlelist_2580031350_7_1.html">易经论坛</a>
